{"id": 141, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在护肤和化妆品上有哪些习惯变化？", "description": "欧莱雅集团的CEO Jean-Paul Agon说上季度美妆市场在短时间内发生骤降，原因是由于消费者开支下降……可明明大家都在买买买啊……", "record_count": 2330, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130051Sn0i4tazCATmx9Z3.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-11-11T16:57:26Z", "questions": [{"id": 122, "title": "你在护肤和化妆品上有哪些习惯变化？", "content": "你在护肤和化妆品上有哪些习惯变化？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1039, "content": "我已经不喜欢清洁力很强的洁面产品了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183122THfKlMagkoYUAF1w.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1040, "content": "我喜欢简单易用的产品，期望一支BB霜搞定全脸", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925428YwLNekEViCjKP6l.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1041, "content": "越来越喜欢化了妆也看不出化了妆的自己", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192543MjaHL7NWmqDV2GIZ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1042, "content": "不太喜欢那些拥有如雷贯耳名声的传统大牌", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192543Ot9aSMDh8nxjlXgu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1043, "content": "我倾向于参考vlogger和明星推荐的产品", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192543s1Weiuw7zng3aMoF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1044, "content": "我会关注cosme大赏之类的护肤品排行榜", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192543wIMjR7P25FXD0VeC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1045, "content": "不爱买全套护肤品，一般只买其中一两件明星产品", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193757iQ3GxA0wVR2NYkPh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1046, "content": "喜欢无添加无刺激的护肤品", "image": "img/option/option/201607031259027WhBd6AGzs0m1Nxy.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}